Kathleen Cody (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kathleen_Cody_(actress) 0 Kathleen Cody (born October 30, 1954), often credited as Kathy Cody, is an American actress. She is best known for her role as the characters Hallie Stokes and Carrie Stokes, on the cult television series Dark Shadows, appearing from June 1970 through April 1971. Her career in film and television encompassed a time period of over 30 years. Kathleen_Cody ( born October_30_,_1954 ) , often_credited as Kathy_Cody , is an_American_actress .
